{"tid":1203183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察應該除低裝備走向市民一方推返個波比政府！","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:00.000Z","uid":79181,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c90eedb43fae0808c770e70f3f5c2228dc761c29","tid":1203183,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"如果連依一步都唔敢行<br />\n就唔好係度煽情話自己內心矛盾<br />\n因為你已經唔係香港人<br />\n你係大陸公安！<br />\n你冇思考係維穩工具！<br />\n大陸公安應該返大陸住！<br />\n而家回頭是岸仲會有和理非支持你地<br />\n<br />\n你班警察自己諗下<br />\n冇必要同自己長大既地方對立！<br />\n如果你落場就代表你選擇毀滅依個你由細到大生活既地方！<br />\n而示威者只係選擇去保護我地香港既核心價值！<br />\n你地自己曾經都係香港一份子<br />\n點解有人唔做要做冇思考既機器比人利用<br />\n想一世人諗住打死一份工？<br />\n你地冇諗過<br />\n到時大陸唔信你地將警察換晒做支那人會點？"},{"pid":"14c65819042e0c0383d9f7338b42936256b323b6","tid":1203183,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2970c9c876036d64e08d2aa924adcdc473874c18","tid":1203183,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b722330db7fd06412acd0dadfdd39102497e019","tid":1203183,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}